    dc:description "Figure 36. Uvariodendron mossambicense Robson ex Dagallier & Couvreur A entire specimen sheet with young branch and leaves B leaf, top view C ' eragrostiform' apical bud D monocarp and flower buds. A-D Mendonca 2558 A (type). Photos Leo-Paul Dagallier." ;
